    • Method Detail

      • convert

        public Map<String,Object> convert(AssociationType1 association)
        This method creates a Map representation of the AssociationType1 provided. The following keys will be added to the map (Taken from EbrimConstants):

        ASSOCIATION_TYPE = "associationType"; SOURCE_OBJECT = "sourceObject"; TARGET_OBJECT = "targetObject";

        This will also try to parse RegistryObjectType values to the map.

        Parameters:
        association - the AssociationType1 to be converted into a map, null returns empty Map
        Returns:
        Map representation of the AssociationType1 provided
